title: New Update: She's Packing Up And Leaving Her Boyfriend...Without Him Knowing
description:
Remember our listener who set an unspoken date of when she wanted to be engaged. When the date expired, she packed up her things and moved out while her boyfriend was out of town. He was upset when returned home and gave a list of reasons why he hadn't proposed yet.
It's been well over a year since we last heard from our listener, and we need an update. Are they still together? Did he ever propose? Listen!
